|中國國家主席]][[習近平|習近平]]向韓國總統致以慰問電話<ref>{{cite news|title=习近平就韩国客轮沉没事故向韩国总统致慰问电|publisher=[[新華網|新華網]]|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2014-04/17/c_1110291453.htm|date=2014-04-17|accessdate=2014-04-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140420104253/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2014-04/17/c_1110291453.htm|archivedate=2014-04-20}}{{zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/mfa_eng/zxxx_662805/t1148345.shtml |title=Xi Jinping Sends Message of Condolences to ROK President over Accident of the Sinking of the ROK Passenger Ship |publisher=[[中華人民共和國外交部|中華人民共和國外交部]] |date=2014-04-17 |accessdate=2014-05-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140508080341/http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/mfa_eng/zxxx_662805/t1148345.shtml |archivedate=2014-05-08 }}{{en}}</ref>。[[越南社會主義共和國主席|越南國家主席]][[張晉創|張晉創]]與政府副總理兼外交部長[[范平明|范平明]]等人向[[韓國外交部|韓國外交部]]部長[[尹炳世|尹炳世]]慰問<ref>{{cite news |last=Kim |first=KwonYoung (권용) |url=http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/bulletin/2014/04/17/0200000000AKR20140417197800084.HTML |title=<여객선침몰> 베트남 "인명피해에 깊은 애도" |publisher=[[韓國聯合通訊社|韓國聯合通訊社]] |date=2014-04-17 |accessdate=2014-04-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419011615/http://www.yonhapnews.co.kr/bulletin/2014/04/17/0200000000AKR20140417197800084.HTML |archivedate=2014-04-19 }}{{ko}}</ref>。[[英國外交大臣|英國外交大臣]][[威廉·黑格|威廉·黑格]]對客船沉没表示哀悼<ref>{{cite web|title=南韓客輪沉沒 英外相表哀悼|url=http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=101522|publisher=[[中央廣播電臺|中央廣播電臺]]|work=[[中央社|中央社]]|date=2014-04-18|accessdate=2014-04-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418234142/http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=101522|archivedate=2014-04-18}}{{zh}}</ref>。[[方濟各_(教宗)|方濟各教宗]]以[[國務院_(聖座)|聖座國務院]]名義向韓國天主教主教團致慰問電<ref>{{cite news|author=李顺兴|title=[韩沉船惨案]教皇及各国首脑相继吊唁|url=http://cnnews.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2014/04/18/20140418000008.html|accessdate=2014-04-18|newspaper=[[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]]中文版|date=2014年4月18日|publisher=《[[朝鮮日報|朝鮮日報]]》|location=[[首爾|首爾]]|dead