許多國際主流媒體也對韓國[[公共安全|公共安全]]和無法理解的長幼文化表達強烈看法。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》報導，這場災難「讓教育年輕人尊重老一代的[[儒家|儒家]]文化顯得異常刺眼」、「看起來像是[[第三世界|第三世界]]的災難」<ref>{{cite news |last=Demick |first=Barbara |url=http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-south-korea-calamity-20140423-story.html |title=Ferry disaster fills South Korea with shame |date=2014-04-22 |accessdate=2018-06-01 |newspaper=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |archive-date=2018-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508192816/http://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-south-korea-calamity-20140423-story.html |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>。[[路透通訊社|路透通訊社]]表示：「許多孩子並沒有質疑他們的長輩，這是一種韓國社會的階級式傳統，他們為了順從而付出生命代價」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-korea-ship-idUSBREA3F01Y20140422?feedType=RSS&feedName=topNews&utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter&dlvrit=992637 |title=First sign of South Korea ferry disaster was call from a frightened boy |work=[[路透社|路透社]] |date=2014-04-22 |accessdate=2018-06-01 |archive-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219134418/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-korea-ship-idUSBREA3F01Y20140422?feedType=RSS&feedName=topNews&utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter&dlvrit=992637 |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>。《{{link-en|達拉斯晨報|The Dallas Morning News}}》認為：「如果那是一大堆美國學生，你知道他們會用任何方式逃離這艘船。但在亞洲文化中，每個人都要服從團體的要求，因此守規矩是非常必要的。所以，你最終會因順從而遭受這種可怕的死亡」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.dallasnews.com/opinion/opinion/2014/04/21/south-korean-freighter-death-by-obedience |title=South Korean ferry: death by obedience |work={{link-en|達拉斯晨報|The Dallas Morning News}} |date=2014-04-21 |accessdate=2018-06-01 |archive-date=2019-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510090536/https://www.dallasnews.com/opinion/opinion/2014/04/21/south-korean-freighter-death-by-obedience |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>。《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》指出：「韓國青少年非常習慣被告知該做什麼以及該怎麼想」<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.scmp.com/news/asia/article/1486408/culture-obedience-scrutinized-following-korean-ferry-disaster |title=Culture of obedience scrutinized following Korean ferry disaster |work=[[南華早報|南華早報]] |date=2014-04-17 |accessdate=2018-06-01 |archive-date=2017-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808093918/http://www.scmp.com/news/asia/article/1486408/culture-obedience-scrutinized-following-korean-ferry-disaster |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>。[[CNN|CNN]]表示：「這種文化一直鼓勵晚輩對長輩百依百順，所以當成年人要求學生原地待命時，他們當然會照做」。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》則認為不應該將這起事故歸咎於韓國文化，政府結構的問題才是最嚴重的罪魁禍首<ref>{{cite news |url=http://time.com/75742/south-korea-ferry-asian-stereotypes-culture-blaming/ |title=Culture Blaming and Stereotyping in the South Korean Ferry Tragedy |work=[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]] |date=2014-04-25 |accessdate=2018-06-01 |archive-date=2018-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525095602/http://time.com/75742/south-korea-ferry-asian-stereotypes-culture-blaming/ |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>。

